---
title: Sơ đồ tuần tự — Đăng nhập JWT và chọn tenant
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(Next.js)
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>/auth/login
    participant SVC as AuthService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: nhập email + password
    FE->>+API: POST /auth/login
    API->>+SVC: authenticate(email, pw)
    SVC->>DB: SELECT user JOIN memberships
    DB-->>SVC: user + tenant_ids
    Note right of SVC: bcrypt.checkpw(pw, hashed)
    SVC-->>-API: jwt_token (exp 1h)
    API-->>-FE: 200 OK — access_token + memberships

    Note over FE: Zustand tenant-store.setTenant(tenant_ids[0])<br/>axios interceptor inject X-Tenant-Id

    FE->>+API: GET /members/me<br/>Auth: Bearer <jwt>, X-Tenant-Id: <tid>
    Note right of API: Dependency:<br/>require_customer_in_tenant<br/>(hoặc require_owner_in_tenant)
    API-->>-FE: member profile
    FE-->>U: render dashboard
